text: This bus stop is honestly a little awkwardly located. It's quite important because it brings you to Somerset 313 and Orchard Takashimaya / Paragon. But, there's also no sheltered walkway, so if it rains, you're pretty much done. That said, it's clean and well, many people drop and board here for said reasons above.
Suitably spacious.. easy route to Apple Store and other locations.
SD$1.50 cash per short bus trip
